(1, 3, 'Lemon Tree Premier', 1, 'Check-in time: 14:00\r\nCheck-out time: 00:00', 'Opposite Mittal Industrial Estate, Andheri - Kurla Rd, Andheri East, Mumbai, Maharashtra 400059\r\n', '022 6825 1111'),
(2, 8, 'Hotel Pearl International', 6, 'A 10-minute walk from Chennai Central railway station, this informal hotel with a glass facade is 4 km from the Government Museum and 3 km from 17th-century Fort St. George.\r\nFeaturing tiled floors, the down-to-earth rooms offer free Wi-Fi and flat-screen TVs, plus tea and coffeemaking facilities. Some include minifridges. Suites add dining areas. Room service is available.\r\n\r\nA breakfast buffet is complimentary. There\'s also an international restaurant and an exercise room, as well as a business centre and meeting space. Parking is available.\r\n\r\nCheck-in time: 00:00\r\nCheck-out time: 00:00', '39, VV Koil Street, Opp Canara Bank, Park Town, Periyamet, Periyamet,Chennai, Tamil Nadu 600003', '044 2561 5959'),
(3, 9, 'Taj Lands End Mumbai', 1, 'Overlooking the Arabian Sea, this high-end hotel is 3.3 km from Bandra train station and 7.8 km from the Bandra Kurla Complex business center.\r\nTraditional rooms with sea views feature Wi-Fi, desks, and tea and coffeemaking facilities. Club-level rooms and suites provide butler service and access to a lounge with free breakfast and evening cocktails. Plush suites add separate living rooms, and some offer whirlpool tubs.\r\n\r\nDining options include Indian, Chinese and Italian restaurants, as well as a sophisticated lobby lounge. There is also an outdoor pool, a hot tub, a spa and a fitness center, plus a 24-hour business center and 4 meeting rooms.\r\n\r\nCheck-in time: 14:00\r\nCheck-out time: 12:00', 'Band Stand, BJ Road, Mount Mary, Bandra West, Mumbai, Maharashtra 400050', '022 6668 1234'),
(4, 10, 'Royal Lancaster London', 9, 'Situated above Lancaster Gate tube station, this upscale hotel overlooking Hyde Park is 0.3 miles from Paddington tube and train station, offering direct links to Heathrow airport.\r\nPolished rooms have flat-screen TVs and free Wi-Fi. Upgraded rooms add sitting areas, desks and park views. Suites provide iPod docks and Nespresso machines.\r\n\r\nAmenities include a warm all-day restaurant offering European dishes and park views, a Thai-themed restaurant serving afternoon tea, and an airy lobby bar. There is also a 24-hour exercise room. Business facilities include conference suites and meeting rooms. Breakfast is available for a fee.\r\n\r\nCheck-in time: 03:00\r\nCheck-out time: 12:00', 'Lancaster Terrace, London W2 2TY, United Kingdom', '+44 20 7551 600');
